content: Nope. It's on. You should get a text and email with everything you need a little before it starts (usually about 30 mins)

Hi <@1276944250491113656> --I was about 30 minutes into the text training when my laptop ran out of battery; so frustrating! I missed the last portion, which I understand included the quiz that will allow me to text with you all. I am a very experienced texter, having been at this since Team Joe and Victory 2020, along with Beto's senate/gubernatorial campaigns and Powered by People. Presently a text mod with Campaign for Democracy as well. Is there any way you can send me that quiz link, or do I need to sit for the whole training again?

<@1115406116910813234> I don't have that capacity in my roles, but you can post a question in the <#1267941954243526756> and tag @ sophiatroutman and see if she can help you. You might also DM her and ask if she can send you her calendly link for a 15 minute 1-on-1 to override the quiz portion. Sorry it's been such a hassle.
